{"tid":1496484,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"[連住尼PLEASE COME]希望改一改BLOCK USER 當中既小小設定","createTime":"2019-08-22T14:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T14:19:25.000Z","uid":110509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"85058d8c90189a1d77d3d0b97e480f8c80dc0a79","tid":1496484,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:19:25.000Z","msg":"封鎖用戶有分<br />\n(1)普通封鎖<br />\n(2)完全封鎖<br />\n<br />\n遇到5毛正常會封鎖佢, 但當封鎖左佢就見唔到佢出過既POST, 咁個5毛就可以繼續帶風向, BLOCK 左佢既USER 就提醒唔到其他人小心5毛樓主既言論<br />\n<br />\n所以, 希望連仔 為封鎖用戶功能作出以下修改:<br />\n睇到佢出既POST, 但入到去會顯示&quot;封鎖用戶&quot;<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以睇下個5毛講D 咩而去提醒其他人<br />\n如果連佢出既POST 都唔想顯示既人會選擇 &quot; 完全封鎖&quot;<br />\n<br />\n打緊仗, 唔該連仔盡快改左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}